  "body": "If run this query\r\n```graphql\r\n  block {\r\n    tooShort: account(address:\"0xffff\") {\r\n      balance\r\n    }\r\n    notHexadecimal: account(address: \"foobarbaz\") {\r\n      balance\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n```\r\nIt returns zero for both accounts. It should return an error as it works in the console\r\n```\r\n> eth.getBalance('0xfff')\r\nError: invalid address\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `1.9.0-stable`\r\nOS & Version: OSX",
